title: Bruce Springsteen 100 Greatest Songs - Rolling Stone Magazine
description:
Plus 20 more that should have made it.  Songs 1-100 are rated from the magazine, and songs 101 - 120 are my choices in random order.  Some of RS's choices are a bit perplexing, ie...Jack of All Trades, but nonetheless it's a very enjoyable list.  

I am not saying this torrent is perfect, there may be metadata not exact.  I just wanted to get this torrent out - I've spent enough time on it.  

I tried to reduce the file size to no avail.  Went from FLAC Level 4 to Level 7, and the file size was roughly the same.
